Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.30,0:00:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在被星光照射的頂屋裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.90,0:00:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,獨自一人聆聽著天空的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.55,0:00:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用玻璃的繃帶遮住眼睛行走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.20,0:00:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都是孤獨的馬戲團孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.85,0:00:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,孤身一人的悲傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.10,0:00:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,震動的繃帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.87,0:00:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,撼動著心靈……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.35,0:01:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用溫柔的眼神期待與某人的相會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.05,0:01:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我耳邊細語「請留在我身邊」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.27,0:01:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Silent Voice
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.39,0:01:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,救起奇怪的貨船後\n我們又救起拉莎拉和莎拉莎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.73,0:01:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,意外地,貨船上竟然隱藏了MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.39,0:01:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由於莫迪的活耀表現\n我們才擊退敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.53,0:01:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回想起來\n月月的兩位小姐好像成了我和哈曼之間的防護罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.24,0:01:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在我乃不知道哈曼在我附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.07,0:02:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第四十話\n老虎巴姆之夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.98,0:02:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼他們這麼討厭我們?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.58,0:02:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,右邊,往右邊避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.25,0:02:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇斯\n他說右邊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.00,0:02:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你閉嘴,靜靜看著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.74,0:02:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們已經發出訊號了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.38,0:02:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個,那個\n你吵死了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.55,0:02:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行,來不及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.26,0:02:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放下防禦幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.44,0:02:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會...會被擊中的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.95,0:02:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻擊魚雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.17,0:02:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.18,0:03:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是最後一個嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.37,0:03:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏不是中立空域嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.67,0:03:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你以為戰爭時\n有那麼簡單中立嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.80,0:03:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.61,0:03:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好豪華的殖民地啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.59,0:03:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是以舊世紀的香港為模仿對象的殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.63,0:03:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.26,0:03:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打開通訊回答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.64,0:03:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打開艦橋!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.51,0:03:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們不知道考慮巴姆的入境條件嗎!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.87,0:03:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,入境條件?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.32,0:03:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我代替史丹巴總監警告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.04,0:03:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新亞加瑪的船員和\n平名在內都一定要下船...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.21,0:03:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹什麼?\n走開!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.00,0:04:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.05,0:04:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MS也不准動用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.40,0:04:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禁止開炮\n別開玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.06,0:04:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才若不開炮\n我們的艦橋就被魚雷擊破了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.34,0:04:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走開!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.50,0:04:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等\n幹什麼連這裏也要貼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.65,0:04:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以上是入境條件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.47,0:04:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼嚴嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.09,0:04:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,貼上的封條是絕對不准撕下的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.17,0:04:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼大人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.70,0:04:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別在意,這是瞭解\n一般市民作風的好機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.74,0:04:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,檢查完後立刻下船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.08,0:04:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高達嗎?這個值錢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.88,0:04:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新亞加瑪...\n-被繩子給綁著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.99,0:04:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是你們停留期間與人開戰\n那我們就無琺中立了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.78,0:04:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不會做那種事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.80,0:05:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽著,我們總監史丹巴大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.86,0:05:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直致力於讓殖民地\n成為永遠沒有戰火的殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.93,0:05:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史丹普?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.05,0:05:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是史丹巴大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.40,0:05:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們老虎巴姆殖民地\n被治理成一大觀光地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.49,0:05:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這都歸功於\n史丹巴閣下英明領導
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.69,0:05:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來他是遊樂園的園長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.50,0:05:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.54,0:05:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遊樂園不是和平的象徵嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.16,0:05:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.47,0:05:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.31,0:05:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要去哪裏?\n進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.95,0:05:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算是中立殖民地\n也應該說清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.24,0:05:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我剛才全都說清楚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.65,0:05:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你太霸道了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.96,0:05:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.52,0:05:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是那邊,你們到那邊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.58,0:05:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我早有聽聞\n想不到竟是這麼有風格的殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.03,0:05:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.75,0:06:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才想上巴士的是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.87,0:06:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.15,0:06:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不是船員,抓到也沒用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.69,0:06:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是要跟高達交換嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.48,0:06:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要抓對人才有用啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.31,0:06:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這女人\n看起來似乎很倔強,很有勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.68,0:06:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帶這女人來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.99,0:06:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我喜歡帶來有衝勁的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.24,0:06:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.65,0:06:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.84,0:06:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.03,0:06:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼,普通的裝飾品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.27,0:06:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你快搭上那班巴士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.17,0:06:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是右邊的巴士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.18,0:06:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?看不見啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.58,0:06:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你搭左邊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.98,0:06:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.98,0:06:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.50,0:06:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可口的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.37,0:06:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.88,0:06:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差點被看出監視攝影機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.50,0:06:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼回事!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.00,0:06:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼要把人分開?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.60,0:06:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該能自由行動吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.97,0:06:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.67,0:07:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位,他們能接納我們\n我們就該存感謝之心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.07,0:07:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是你們的做法也有可議之處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.06,0:07:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實你只要說出理由\n我們就會遵從的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.72,0:07:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏是和平的殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.95,0:07:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們必須對軍人加以監視
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.13,0:07:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才要分類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.92,0:07:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了,我們確實有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.46,0:07:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莎拉莎...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.98,0:07:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們...\n又發現好女人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.98,0:07:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該還有更美的,再找找吧\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.78,0:07:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎辦?露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.45,0:07:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莎拉莎說的對,艾莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.71,0:07:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,把他們都帶過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.61,0:07:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.29,0:07:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把男人給我分開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.46,0:07:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.80,0:07:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個殖民地的長官叫史丹巴吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.41,0:07:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.51,0:07:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的品味不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.09,0:07:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.04,0:07:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是亞加瑪救起的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.58,0:08:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也被派上這輛車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.58,0:08:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這殖民地很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.29,0:08:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.80,0:08:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許這是光之神的決定吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.65,0:08:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.69,0:08:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.61,0:08:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣任人擺佈好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.50,0:08:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們只能暫時觀望了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.55,0:08:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾莉他們不知要不要緊呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.49,0:08:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.96,0:08:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們到專用宿舍去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.72,0:08:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.87,0:08:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麻煩你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.00,0:08:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他想幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.45,0:08:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.67,0:08:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.26,0:08:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勉強還可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.34,0:08:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小子,你們想幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.55,0:08:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全體下車,乖乖聽從指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.35,0:08:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不然的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.98,0:08:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.62,0:08:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是怎麼一回事??
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.77,0:08:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要捉你們當人質
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.26,0:08:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到外面來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.33,0:08:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人質?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.37,0:08:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大叔,你快想辦法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.27,0:09:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他昏的真是合時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.60,0:09:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想反抗嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.98,0:09:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你以為你這麼做!\n我會照辦嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.73,0:09:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.80,0:09:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?\n可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.62,0:09:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乖乖把高達交出來\n什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.40,0:09:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓開\n乖一點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.44,0:09:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.43,0:09:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.68,0:09:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.13,0:09:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站著!可惡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.73,0:09:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小子,我不會讓你輕易逃走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.16,0:09:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放...放開我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.67,0:09:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想偷高達?\n放開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.85,0:09:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是史丹巴要求的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.80,0:09:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.73,0:09:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個也抓住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.46,0:09:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們只是想要MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.72,0:09:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才不是史丹巴的手下!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.92,0:09:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要MS做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.84,0:09:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然是拿去賣錢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.54,0:09:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,賣?\n不然我們付不出稅金的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.43,0:10:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,稅金?原來是為了付稅金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.62,0:10:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.97,0:10:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算是小孩子\n不付稅金就會被送去礦山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.50,0:10:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的殖民地就是這種地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.04,0:10:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其他女人被送上別的巴士對吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.24,0:10:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史丹巴喜歡挑選美女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.66,0:10:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,送到他的後宮去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.80,0:10:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.99,0:10:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個後宮在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.85,0:10:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說詳細點\n是真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.63,0:10:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說就是了\n你放了我才能說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.05,0:10:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很破舊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.10,0:10:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.61,0:10:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們要去哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.24,0:10:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們是歡迎的客人\n快來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.04,0:10:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沙拉莎\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.72,0:10:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收藏那種MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.64,0:11:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史丹巴到底有什麼陰謀?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.60,0:11:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿斯蘭治他們沒問題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.01,0:11:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.24,0:11:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有阿爾賓他們帶路\n已經去地下旅館了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.22,0:11:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留在這裏不是比較好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.44,0:11:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,回去新亞加瑪最好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.49,0:11:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,只有我們的話\n當作全體被綁架就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.02,0:11:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個很美啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.38,0:11:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我先聲明\n我們不是受你們指使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.47,0:11:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是想給史丹巴看看顏色\n才協助你們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.61,0:11:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.79,0:11:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,洋裝?\n我討厭這打扮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.04,0:11:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉沙拉有危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.60,0:11:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣打扮很漂亮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.95,0:11:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別用奇怪眼光看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.95,0:11:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再慢吞吞啊\n我們的船可能被辛吉翁發現而發展成戰爭的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.93,0:11:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,魯南...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.75,0:11:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎會呢?\n可是我們甚至連逃出這裏的錢都沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.76,0:11:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才要\n從史丹巴的口袋挖錢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.18,0:11:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧\n魯南!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.09,0:12:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,我們也走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.78,0:12:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫我們來這種地方幹什麼啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.90,0:12:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到亞加瑪船上\n有這麼多美女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.99,0:12:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這表示說\n我也能以我的魅力控制亞加瑪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.76,0:12:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們能住在這舒適地方\n或許是光的引導
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.36,0:12:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姊姊是想拯救你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.88,0:12:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你的好意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.02,0:12:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問你想怎樣救我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.56,0:12:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的心理隱藏著秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.89,0:12:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓那秘密暴露在陽光下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.39,0:12:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用你管\n請別再說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.93,0:12:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一再欺騙自己\n是永遠見不到陽光的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.67,0:13:00.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想與這些奇怪的人\n住在同一房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.03,0:13:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再給我一間房間吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.27,0:13:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.60,0:13:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照她的話做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.37,0:13:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.68,0:13:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.29,0:13:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把那女人保留到最後\n先要最鮮嫩的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.47,0:13:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸媽媽死掉後我們無家可歸\n姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.94,0:13:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.38,0:13:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們姐妹不太像啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.66,0:13:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以拜託叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.31,0:13:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我們在史丹巴大人這裏工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.75,0:13:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還太小了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.21,0:13:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我什麼都肯做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.49,0:13:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且最年長的,長的不夠可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.38,0:13:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好過份,太過份了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.29,0:13:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別傷心,長的粗壯也有工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.81,0:13:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帶她們進去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.52,0:13:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你,叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.52,0:13:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.53,0:13:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也進去\n這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.22,0:14:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,那邊也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.07,0:14:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個能用啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.49,0:14:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?\n沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.78,0:14:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MS真不少啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.81,0:14:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓你們久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.97,0:14:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史丹巴大人很快會駕臨的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.84,0:14:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那之前...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.88,0:14:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不先請我們喝杯茶,好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.50,0:14:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們獲邀到大人的後宮\n還囉唆這麼多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.99,0:14:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.40,0:14:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎到我的城堡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.91,0:14:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,美麗的小姐\n都會受到我誠心招待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.06,0:14:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.10,0:14:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必要時就動手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.81,0:14:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏交給姊姊處理吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.96,0:14:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是衷心歡迎你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.87,0:14:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,你的心是封閉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.29,0:14:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.92,0:15:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,健康的心才能看到光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.49,0:15:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,充滿慾望與惡意的心\n是看不到光明的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.89,0:15:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有\n給予那種人幫忙也是一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.41,0:15:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來\n所以請打開你的心看清楚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.86,0:15:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會看清楚的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.00,0:15:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大人,你沒事吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.37,0:15:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不會敲門的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.62,0:15:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道你站在門口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.81,0:15:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.35,0:15:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實是這樣的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.98,0:15:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼醜女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.08,0:15:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她們自願來後宮的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.74,0:15:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒父沒母無家可歸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.60,0:15:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你...捷...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.27,0:15:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莎拉莎,我們到那邊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.11,0:15:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒徵詢我允許\n就放這些人進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.50,0:15:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.75,0:15:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的\n這女孩跟那個留下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.95,0:15:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個醜女給我趕出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.56,0:15:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.61,0:15:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼...\n這聲音也很難聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.26,0:16:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪的人走掉了\n我們繼續吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.68,0:16:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼打扮成這樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.88,0:16:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很適合吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.47,0:16:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別哭了,被趕走比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.86,0:16:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰知道留下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.31,0:16:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你會被強迫做什麼事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.61,0:16:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別那麼沮喪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.02,0:16:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要怪我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.40,0:16:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家等著吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.39,0:16:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才的女孩子...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.69,0:16:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.83,0:16:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被發現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.39,0:16:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.59,0:16:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.14,0:16:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鎖匙嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.10,0:16:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不許動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.63,0:16:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.10,0:16:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.49,0:16:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點\n知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.08,0:17:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.93,0:17:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.66,0:17:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他在幹什麼?\n魯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.76,0:17:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會一直看你們臉色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.16,0:17:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有槍聲,你們沒聽見嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.43,0:17:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,外觀很老舊\n可是駕駛艙是新的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.42,0:17:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不是收藏品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.33,0:17:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小艇,小艇,快準備小艇\n知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.64,0:17:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老虎巴姆的象徵\n需要你們這麼美的女性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.68,0:17:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是伊萊說的事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.67,0:17:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.65,0:17:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚...什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.90,0:17:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的MS阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.89,0:17:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰在開動?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.17,0:17:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這感覺...是捷度.桑捷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.48,0:17:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛...這MS的操縱真難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.15,0:17:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.95,0:18:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是暴動,幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.05,0:18:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史...史丹巴大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.60,0:18:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.80,0:18:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾莉,在哪裏?露卡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.76,0:18:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,在這裏啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.74,0:18:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個窗戶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.96,0:18:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.87,0:18:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你退後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.59,0:18:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.14,0:18:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,動作快點啊\n這地方是經不起襲擊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.00,0:18:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做的好啊,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.63,0:18:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人數目很多啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.82,0:18:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要礙我的事!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.04,0:18:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼MS?這個虐待狂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.82,0:18:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼會?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.41,0:19:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的動作怎麼會這麼快的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.45,0:19:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要你知道外表不等於實力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.69,0:19:18.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我,魯南!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.75,0:19:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是比查嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.13,0:19:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史丹巴在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.54,0:19:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要抓住他,勒索一筆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.39,0:19:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,後面啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.89,0:19:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像很強啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.61,0:19:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.88,0:19:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,魯南...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.21,0:19:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.11,0:19:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,魯南,快逃\n實力相差太遠了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.87,0:19:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.05,0:19:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想和我打嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.71,0:19:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度.桑捷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.68,0:19:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這聲音...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.59,0:20:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是哈曼嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.10,0:20:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又見面了,捷度.桑捷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.34,0:20:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼你會在這裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.82,0:20:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想再和你談一次話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.35,0:20:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才來見你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.63,0:20:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽從我的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.53,0:20:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣我便承認你是新人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.03,0:20:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓你免於白死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.67,0:20:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才不會白死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.73,0:20:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還不知道嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.83,0:20:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我當然知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.20,0:20:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們大人掀起的戰爭\n總是拖累所有人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.80,0:20:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說話太天真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.05,0:20:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才不喜歡\n去討大人的歡心啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.17,0:20:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.23,0:20:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯,你不敢殺人\n你是可愛的小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.31,0:21:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.26,0:21:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.23,0:21:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼哈曼會來這裏的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.31,0:21:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差點便成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.18,0:21:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史丹巴那些愚蠢東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.75,0:21:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,船員被綁架\n你們的警備令我無法放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.07,0:21:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是入境條件...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.11,0:21:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.73,0:21:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會外出了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.45,0:21:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請讓我做啟航準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.76,0:21:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.26,0:21:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,魯南,沒問題吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.12,0:21:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.49,0:21:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼會救我們的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.58,0:21:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們讓我學到很多東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.32,0:21:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,學?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.72,0:21:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是史丹巴的霸道\n使得老虎巴姆捲入戰火的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.59,0:21:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,請小心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.87,0:21:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個殖民地已經被惡念襲捲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.80,0:21:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.86,0:21:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個惡念急速擴大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.71,0:21:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是因為哈曼嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.70,0:22:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,應該是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.34,0:22:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.21,0:22:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之前哈曼的惡意\n怎麼沒傷到捷度他們的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.39,0:22:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是由於我們的保護
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.58,0:22:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.53,0:22:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大人的邪惡重疊過多時\n清高美麗的花朵很有可能被壓潰的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.30,0:22:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成百 成萬 上億的繁星啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.49,0:22:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何只是閃耀而已 展示你言語的能力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.55,0:23:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在我也能不回頭地 讓心靈出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.70,0:23:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若能把多如繁星的生命儲存的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.65,0:23:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把整個銀河也化作光芒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.35,0:23:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,化作緊握在掌心的 生命的重量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.32,0:23:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我仍未能看見宇宙的路標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.22,0:23:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,手掌觸摸著一千萬年的光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.39,0:23:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼預料到了我們試圖離開史丹巴的殖民衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.76,0:23:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果出不去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.81,0:23:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其後 史丹巴駕駛MS攻過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.91,0:23:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這小孩一般的……不對  嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.14,0:24:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒙德 別太冒險了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.70,0:24:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一個敵人要出來了！不能哭著作戰啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.89,0:24:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下集 高達ZZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.73,0:24:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉莎拉的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.37,0:24:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莎拉莎 你真是冷靜呢

